data.description: Enchanting, 2079 sq.ft., 4 bed, 2.5 bath home on an intimate lot in a coveted neighborhood. This cozy abode boasts a main-level office, ideal for remote work or study, as well as an indulgent primary suite, offering a luxurious private retreat upstairs. Sunlit interiors feature a gas-burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Recent updates include new flooring throughout. The fully fenced backyard offers privacy and a peaceful space. Enjoy proximity to amenities, shopping, and the community park fostering a close-knit atmosphere. Conviently located less than 2.5 miles to Hwy 3 for easy commuting. Ideal for those seeking a charming, manageable space with the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and a dedicated workspace.
